{"tid":1071001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超稱無意改變單程證制度　亦不宜加入經濟能力審批","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T06:36:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4e967a1869190091ae566b1313ca93612d7912c6","tid":1071001,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1448847_1_L_20190321110011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1448847_1_L_20190321110011.jpg&h=188853f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會續會辯論改革移民及入境政策無約束力的議案，保安局局長李家超重申，無意改變現有單程證制度的運行。<br />\n<br />\n李家超說，特區政府一向重視社會各界就內地居民來港事宜提出的意見，會密切留意配額使用的情況，並會顧及社會的整體利益，繼續就事宜與內地當局交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n李家超強調，單程證制度不宜加入經濟能力審批條件及甄選識別，重申單程證制度是讓合資格人士有秩序來港團聚，若加入經濟審查，會不符合家庭團聚的政策目標。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，單程證制度客觀及透明，內地居民只要符合內地當局的審批准則，便可以申請來港定居，按年齡及與在港家人分隔時間，定出先後次序。"},{"pid":"97dd7a274462d0110c79822ff9f841287e2a5bb8","tid":1071001,"uid":29080,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8255d7f09168a89ae323c5e4b01c5aaa0ee8a5b","tid":1071001,"uid":82052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97dd7a274462d0110c79822ff9f841287e2a5bb8","tid":1071001,"uid":29080,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490dba7f4b513bb2ea5bd123eadfceee32ab661","tid":1071001,"uid":130695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"佢係咪講漏左 係要顧及大陸社會福利情況"},{"pid":"5cfe763fe00419a568212a8da940c26803fcad9e","tid":1071001,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:14:44.000Z",